            <h3>Methodology</h3>
            <ul class="listing2">
                <li>Learning outcomes - program goals</li>
                <li>Both are a mixture of knowledge, skills and attitudes.</li>
                <li>Emergent curriculum - Planning activities with the children. Children choose what they would like to do or
express an interest. Teachers consider how that idea can be used to extend learning.</li>
                <li>It is not all choice. Teachers will introduce concepts if they see a need or gap in the program.</li>

            </ul>
