            <h3>Philosophy</h3>
            <ul class="listing2">
                <li>The Explorers Kindergarten Program is consistent with the early education program offered in each of
our other rooms. It flows directly from our philosophy incorporating:</li>
                <li>A play -based learning program, designed to stimulate children's love of learning and social connections.</li>
                <li>A welcoming environment for whole families, where siblings may visit and parents contributions of ideas
and interests are valued. Flexibility to incorporate family needs — enrolment up to five days with flexible
arrival and departure times within the operating hours.</li>
                <li>Qualified Teachers and Educators, who role model lifelong learning and nurture children as individuals.</li>
                <li>A program that explores the children's place as citizens in the local and world community.</li>
